### `AgentDock.jsx` (480 lines)

**Sticky Input Bar** (global query entry point):

```javascript
<div className="fixed bottom-0 left-0 right-0 z-30">
  <AgentControlPulse active={pulseActive}>
    <div className="bg-white rounded-[20px] shadow-sm">
